{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Rust Moon of Castia is classic fantasy adventure; a world of heroes and adventurers fighting for fortune and glory under the dangerous gaze of an evil overlord and bickering nations. They can be heroes, mercenaries for hire, or free wheeling adventurers just trying to find the next lost treasure horde. It is always best to work with players when deciding on what kind of fantasy campaign to run because tastes can vary wildly.\par}
